<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="15" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1436,978,1867]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[201,323,1734,1759]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" reason="1">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
This new species can be distinguished from its congeners by the very broad and heavily sclerotized pleural lobes of the eighth abdominal segment, the broad subtriangular valva, and the shuttle-shaped valvella arising from base of costa.
</paragraph>
